prompt.en:
**Shape, Repo**
Implement class hierarchy according to the UML diagram and the main() code.

**UML:**
Class Repo: GetShape(shapeType: string, color: string): Shape*, Add(Shape*): void, Remove(info: string): void, PrintAll(): void.
Abstract Class Shape: name: string, GetName(): string.
Classes Circle, Square, Rectangle realize Shape.

**main():**
```cpp
int main()
{
  Repo *m = new Repo();

  m->Add(m->GetShape("Circle", "red"));
  m->Add(m->GetShape("Square", "yellow"));
  m->Add(m->GetShape("Rectangle", "blue"));
  m->Add(m->GetShape("Rectangle", "red"));
  m->Add(m->GetShape("Circle", "green"));

  m->PrintAll();
  m->Remove("Circle");
  m->PrintAll();

  m->Add(new Circle("green"));
  m->Add(new Rectangle("red"));
  m->Remove("red");
  m->PrintAll();

  return 0;
}
```

